ss and excess envelope mixing during\npost-main sequence evolution of stars with higher overshooting potentially\nresults in a metallicity-independent upper luminosity limit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jul 2021 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2021 09:57:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-10"}
