erage Prot and Sph values for 55,232 main-sequence and subgiant FGKM\nstars (out of 159,442 targets), with 24,182 new Prot detections in comparison\nwith McQuillan et al. (2014). The upper edge of the Prot distribution is\nlocated at longer Prot than found previously.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jul 2021 18:36:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 29 Aug 2021 20:39:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-31"}
