 a perception layer and a behavioral layer. Perception\nalgorithms with respect to scene understanding (object detection and tracking,\npose estimation), localization mapping and path planning are thoroughly\ninvestigated. Behavioural part focuses on decision making and human in the loop\ncontrol.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jul 2021 21:01:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-07"}
