x calibrations in them. On the other hand, some outlier\nspectra show strong nebular contamination warning the corresponding parameters\nshould be carefully used. A catalog and a spectral atlas of all the 3,627\noutliers can be found at the link\nhttp://paperdata.china-vo.org/LY_paper/dr5Outlier/dr5Outlier_resource.zip.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Jul 2021 01:23:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-07"}
